Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.33,0:00:04.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:06.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Come over here, Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:10.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, come on! Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.03,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You slept with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.40,0:00:38.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah, we slept together on my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.53,0:00:40.64,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Does that mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.07,0:00:44.31,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,In the past, I would feel hesitant about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.31,0:00:47.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But once I let it happen, it wasn't that big of a deal anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:47.31,Petto_basic_2,Yuri,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:52.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, but we just slept. Got our sleep together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:53.48,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Then what…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.15,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You didn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.38,0:00:57.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of course I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:01:00.16,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Then… while you were sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.93,0:01:06.13,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,it wasn't like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:08.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Nope, not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.03,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,More like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.23,0:01:16.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't know… but I felt warm, and I slept well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:20.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Whenever I sleep with a man, I always feel kind of crammed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:22.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,With Momo, I don't really think about it too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:25.38,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You may feel that way, but are you sure the pet doesn't feel anything either?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.38,0:01:27.85,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Sleeping together, as a man…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:31.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't think so. He was in a deep sleep, and he didn't toss about.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.92,0:01:34.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo is actually pretty well brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.16,0:01:37.26,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He doesn't spill food and he's clean when he uses the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:39.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Maybe because he was a ballerina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.59,0:01:43.63,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,No, maybe that pet doesn't have any interest in women.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:46.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't think it's like that. He had a girlfriend and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.10,0:01:46.94,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,A girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:47.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.87,0:01:50.01,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I'm asking, are you Takeshi's girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:51.21,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Hey, Rumi…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:53.38,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,It's okay. It's over between me and him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.38,0:01:55.81,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Isn't that kind of insolent? For him to have a girlfriend and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:58.41,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Umm… I think it's pretty natural, considering he's a male.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And she's actually kind of pretty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:01.38,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're the one who's abnormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.38,0:02:02.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Abnormal? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:04.99,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Sleeping with your pet before sleeping with your boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Those are two different types of sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.13,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai probably thinks it's strange, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.13,0:02:13.36,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You come home early from your dates saying, "I have to take care of my pet."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.36,0:02:15.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because he's also pretty busy with work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.03,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,And you don't invite him over to your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:21.57,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Sleeping together aside… up till this point, you've only let him kiss you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.30,0:02:24.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Well, that's because…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:27.44,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I knew it, I think you're…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.81,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hmm… What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.85,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Actually, I won't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.52,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,I'm scared if I say it, it'll come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:35.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:41.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Despite how this looks, I am a journalist from a major newspaper publisher.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:44.00,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,About the project on medicine from the last time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:47.30,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,it won the Bureau Chief Award. So here is the report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.66,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.60,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Wow, I can't believe it. Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.60,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.50,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,They want to take a picture of you, so make sure you contact the Business Information center.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.50,0:02:57.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:58.81,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,We did it, Iwaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:03:01.44,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,This is the first time in the last two years, that our department has received the Bureau Chief Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.44,0:03:03.38,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Elites are amazing, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:07.98,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Stop standing there in admiration. Try harder, you men…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.68,0:03:07.98,Petto_basic_2,Ishida,0,0,0,,This is my first time, you know… getting the Bureau Chief Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:11.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Come to think of it… this is my first time as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.42,0:03:15.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Two months ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:18.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was transferred from the External Affairs department to the Lifestyle department,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:20.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'm just starting to get used to the work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.56,0:03:25.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes. I am a cool, hardcore career woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.90,0:03:27.04,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:31.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is my boyfriend, Hasumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.51,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's tall, has a high educational background and a high income.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}What they used to call, the "Top 3", back in those days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:38.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}On top of that, he's sweet and hardworking…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}and a good kisser.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:40.92,Petto_basic_2,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Are you free tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sure, if it's around nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:44.75,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:45.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:04.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the reason I can be this happy is…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:05.91,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.18,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.34,0:04:10.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Momo, the pet I've had for two months now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:14.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Ouch! Will you stop jumping on me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.52,0:04:15.92,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I will not stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:17.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, it hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.95,0:04:20.62,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Do you have any souvenirs for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.49,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What! You didn't bring back any?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:28.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:33.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,There! That's it, OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:35.00,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Whoa! He's bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:37.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:41.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're too noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm 29 soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:47.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know very well that I can't live like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:50.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.69,0:04:56.32,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}For now, I don't want to lose these happy moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.77,title,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Kimi wa petto\NYou are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:06.77,episode,text,0,0,0,,[sign]6. The night my dog bit me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:08.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:12.57,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Next week, some of the departments are getting together for a zengen. Did you all know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:14.48,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,A zengen? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:16.18,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,To put it simply, an employee vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.88,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,It's a term that's used within the newspaper industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.88,0:05:19.81,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,We're with External Affairs, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.72,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:21.72,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Are you kidding? External Affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.95,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Don't say that, chief. Let's all go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.99,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,I don't want to. I don't like the guys from External Affairs, nor those from the Society department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.99,0:05:28.92,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,I can't stand them. I just can't get used to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.03,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Are you going, Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:34.40,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? I don't think I will. I've never gone before, why go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:38.37,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:41.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:45.20,note,text,0,0,0,,[sign]To my comrade, Iwaya-san
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:50.61,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,A performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:53.78,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Yes, it's set in a motif of a Greek myth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.78,0:05:57.49,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I really wanted you to be in it… I wanted you to play the brave youth, Perseus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:06:00.66,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sounds interesting. I'll keep it in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:06.49,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I'm glad. Oh yes, is it true that you haven't applied?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.10,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,To the school in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.30,0:06:09.46,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.73,0:06:11.90,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it totally slipped my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.34,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.77,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,What if you end up not being able to go to Frankfurt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:19.31,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,It's not a privilige that everyone gets to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.48,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.55,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Birdie, you're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.89,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Oh? You're here again, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:33.96,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Lately, he's been coming here every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:38.89,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,I need you to get a grip on yourself, too. You're the ace of our dance company.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:39.50,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.80,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,Oh, about our upcoming performance…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:46.43,Petto_basic,dancer_boss,0,0,0,,If Takeshi can't make it, I'm thinking of assigning you the main role, so please do your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.74,0:06:48.87,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Right, gotcha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:53.91,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I like you… a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:54.81,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:58.45,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait… stop, Junpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.61,0:07:01.05,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Do you mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.05,0:07:03.08,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Yeah, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:07.92,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Then how come during this whole time we've been together, you never made a single move on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:14.03,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Because I'm not that much of a masochist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:20.10,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Huh? Wa… wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.57,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I don't understand what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:26.68,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Hey, Junpei! Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.68,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I can't always be filling in for you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.78,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch, ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.46,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.53,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I had my heart broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.86,0:07:49.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is that so…?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:07:57.90,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That must have been difficult…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:09.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:10.00,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,No, it's over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.52,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.43,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Here is your coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.27,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:40.32,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?! Don't tell me it's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:45.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're kidding me, right? Why such a young girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.12,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,This is your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.12,0:08:48.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:51.63,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It's because you kept seeking advice from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:54.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with me… Besides, you're a doctor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:56.20,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Emily-chan, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.97,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You are the only oasis of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:03.30,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,There, there…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.34,0:09:06.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What does he expect me to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.42,0:09:16.85,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:18.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:22.09,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,That you and the doctor can only love pets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:24.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? No, I'm different…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:25.33,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,But even so, that doctor…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:32.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But, well… how do I say this…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:35.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It is kind of a nuisance to have someone in love with you at your workplace…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:37.57,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,It's not the love that is a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:41.54,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand the fact that he wasn't treating me like a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:45.05,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,He only feels love for creatures that are weaker than him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:48.35,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,He wants to protect them, he wants them to always be by his side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.75,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,But that feeling only comes from feeling superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:56.02,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Basically, the perspective of normal humans towards love is just of a different quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:10:01.53,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I may be soft, but I'm not a pet. That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:11.71,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,A breakdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:16.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's true that all men love big breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.18,0:10:18.05,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.05,0:10:21.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But that's not due to preference. It's because they don't have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:23.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,The reason he is attracted to you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:27.40,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,is that his milled heart is unconditionally drawn to your softness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:31.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not a feeling of superiority. Well, there may be a little of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:35.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But to desire something that you lack, I think it's okay to call that love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:40.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Seeing you from the perspective of even a woman like me, you are excellent and graceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're very charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I said too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:02.12,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.86,0:11:09.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why am I making such a passionate speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.47,0:11:14.40,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Did you hear? For the zengen, we're with the Lifestyle department too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:20.81,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This year, with the war and election for the House of Councilors, many departments cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:22.94,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,There's a possibility of a breakup election as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.05,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,so the Main department probably can't go either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:27.72,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I guess those who can should just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:32.39,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's been a while since I've been on a vacation to Hakone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:32.39,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wonder why they want to go that far…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.26,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:38.83,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya, you don't mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:45.47,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… well, I've never been there either…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.47,0:11:46.77,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:49.24,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I guess…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:56.28,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,employee vacations are pretty boring actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.75,0:12:01.02,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yeah… how boring… hot springs and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:05.39,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,So boring… to have a barbeque with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:11.66,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's boring to have a drink with Iwaya in her yukata…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:12.89,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:24.04,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was thinking… if it was with External Affairs this year, I may go…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:25.80,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.19,0:12:27.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:28.71,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.98,0:12:30.48,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,An employee vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:31.48,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.78,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,That means staying over?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's only for a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:38.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:44.99,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I'm invited to a dance workshop on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,A workshop?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:47.60,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.13,0:12:52.27,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's kind of like a camp-in with the dance company I always go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:56.17,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Instructors come, we take lessons and choreograph.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:12:58.31,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.98,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,If you weren't gonna be around, I should've gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:04.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is it too late to go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:07.92,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think it's past the deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:13.19,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Man, I'll have to stay home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:21.53,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll try to come home as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:24.87,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:28.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't really like those kinds of group activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You feel so soft and nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:52.76,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.99,0:13:53.96,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.96,0:13:56.16,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Hasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:57.17,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Okay, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.01,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You're not going to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:11.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm… it hurts when I get sunburnt.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then, I'll take a rest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, it's okay. You don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:20.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Please have fun with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.43,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:36.47,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,There's no way I can say, "Actually, I've never played tennis before."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.94,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I would never lose in aikidou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:52.79,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wow! It feels like we're underwater, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:54.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:57.76,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san, I heard that there are seals over there. Let's go see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.19,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.37,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Chief didn't come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:10.64,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,He's too stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.37,0:15:17.48,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Never mind about that. Ishida-kun, do you know how to understand women through a barbeque?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:19.91,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,No, what't that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.22,0:15:23.55,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,In this world, humans can be separated into a few categories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:25.09,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,The first is…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.09,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,"Eaters"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:31.23,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,"Cookers"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.83,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,"Those that never cook but get to be served".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:41.34,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.87,0:15:47.14,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Usually, men can't really tell the difference between
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.31,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,the "Cookers" and "those that never cook but get to be served".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:53.38,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,They're happy just by being served,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.38,0:15:56.22,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,so they don't try to delve into the deeper psychology of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:16:00.62,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,On top of that, those who are served and don't cook have a lot of time on their hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:05.13,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,So they can engage in fun conversations and raise the spirit of a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.39,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.93,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That's where the snare is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.93,0:16:11.00,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Man, I still have so much to learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:13.80,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Well, personally I like the Cookers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:18.37,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's true that her movements seem very feminine and family-oriented.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:19.94,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:25.71,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,But you know what? The most hardworking person is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:31.15,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,The dullest type of people, the "Cutters".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:34.76,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Wow, she's cutting. Iwaya-san's cutting a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.06,0:16:37.89,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,The way she cuts is pretty impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:41.10,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yeah, well… I can assure you that she's great at cooking, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:44.77,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Man… I envy you, Hasumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:48.67,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,She really is something. I have so much respect for Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:50.00,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.81,0:16:53.24,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,But that kind of perfect people who can do everything
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.24,0:16:54.84,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,kind of tire you out when you're together, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:58.65,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,It's like you can't relax…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.65,0:17:00.42,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,She does have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.42,0:17:04.79,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,When she gets her work done so well, it becomes hard to warm up to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:06.02,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.02,0:17:08.86,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,She doesn't even let you help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.16,0:17:12.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's fine. I can get more done when I'm doing it by myself anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:16.00,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You know… my skin is so sensitive that
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.00,0:17:19.33,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I can't do any kind of washing unless I have special gloves on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.33,0:17:22.00,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, really? That must be a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.00,0:17:24.57,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I think it's starting to get itchy again…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.88,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I may have some kind of ointment back at the lodge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:30.91,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine. Don't worry about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.18,0:17:38.19,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why is he so nice to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.19,0:17:41.69,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san, I barbequed this meat for you! Please have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.00,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Give me some, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:45.96,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,There are a lot more over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.60,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! Let's all take a picture! Shall we? A picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.30,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Oh, Hasumi-san… move over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.67,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I want to be next to him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.77,0:18:00.20,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san! Why don't you join us in the picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:03.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, I'm sorry. I don't really like pictures very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.61,0:18:05.18,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.32,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Then everyone, come in. Here…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.32,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Over here! Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:13.29,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Everyone pose! Uriyama-san, please raise your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:20.93,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is why I didn't want to come… {\i1}on such a stupid vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:28.24,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Excuse me, this dog brought a letter to an employee in our department.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.21,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, where is Iwaya-san today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:31.74,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,She's on the employee vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:33.91,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.48,0:18:37.65,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Emily, here, here… welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:43.59,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,When they're around, it's loud and obnoxious, but once they're gone, it gets lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.09,0:18:48.12,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you stay and have some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:49.39,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.51,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san, here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.51,0:19:05.17,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.08,0:19:15.95,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,How about you, Iwaya-san? A drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:17.19,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:19.69,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.42,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,A cup?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.47,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Is Momo staying home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:35.47,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:41.48,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,My Carlos, too. But cats can stand one night alone, won't dogs get lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:43.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:45.85,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,But your younger brother can take care of it, can't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.85,0:19:49.48,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,What? A younger brother? Iwaya-san has a younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:52.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Mine is fine. It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:58.83,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,That's so true. Pets actually aren't as lonely as we think they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:19:59.80,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:00.90,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:06.13,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Like the last time she disappeared… when she came back, her fur looked oddly nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.80,0:20:10.41,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I guess they have their own little world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:14.31,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,She probably has a boyfriend. Even though her master doesn't have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:16.28,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,You piss me off, Ishidacchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:18.81,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how Momo's doing…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:22.48,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Man, I have to stay home again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:40.04,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san, I think I'm feeling a little tipsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:49.04,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder why I'm in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:21.38,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Miss, if you are leaving, would you like me to call a taxi for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, that's okay. I can get one myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:29.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Damn…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.96,0:21:42.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,30 more minutes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:46.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Maybe I should just take the bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:18.57,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hello, Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:23.67,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello~?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:25.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.74,0:22:29.11,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Huh? Is something wrong, Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.31,0:22:31.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It can't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:32.05,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.65,0:22:34.32,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hello? Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:36.08,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.08,0:22:38.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Can you hear me, Sumire-chan? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.29,0:22:47.33,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You're kidding me! Sumire-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:49.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.70,0:22:53.80,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Ouch! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.80,0:22:55.40,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan, you smell like sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.40,0:22:57.44,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why are you here, you little rascal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.94,0:22:58.04,Petto_basic_2,Momo,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:22:59.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's what I'd like to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.61,0:23:02.00,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm here for that thing… the dance workshop I told you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.00,0:23:05.28,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,My friend submitted an application for me and they called me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:07.52,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,We're having it at the hall over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:08.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're kidding me, it's so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.72,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I remember you said yours was in Hakone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:16.32,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing here like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.63,0:23:20.86,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The icebreaker was kind of boring, so I stepped out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:26.63,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Were you trying to go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.07,0:23:28.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not really…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.31,0:23:31.51,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:37.01,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Then I'll go home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.01,0:23:40.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You've got to participate in the workshop, so you should stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.38,0:23:42.78,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't matter. I was able to get some tips this afternoon already.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:44.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not okay! Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:46.32,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.46,0:23:54.46,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Sumire-chan, you only have to say the words "Let's go home".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.80,0:23:57.33,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Because you're my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:08.38,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let's go home…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.01,0:24:10.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.32,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute. I'll go grab my stuff right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.69,0:24:27.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:39.31,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hasumi-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.38,0:24:42.14,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I finally found you, Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.61,0:24:49.95,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You suddenly disappeared. Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.72,0:24:56.46,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I decided to sober myself up with a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.26,0:24:58.53,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,With your baggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.53,0:24:58.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.43,0:25:05.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, this… it has material for my work and some valuables.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.37,0:25:07.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,So I was afraid to leave them behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.24,0:25:08.24,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.37,0:25:14.34,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I was worried that you might be angry at me for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.54,0:25:15.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.01,0:25:20.52,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You seemed to be avoiding me during dinner, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.52,0:25:21.75,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're imagining things…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.55,0:25:24.09,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Of course I'm angry…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.09,0:25:26.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm furious about the whole thing with Fukushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:28.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.69,0:25:30.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.13,0:25:34.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was just a little tired, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.00,0:25:37.27,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.20,0:25:39.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.21,0:26:22.31,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Everyone wanted to go for karaoke, so they went out to town.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.08,0:26:25.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.45,0:26:31.19,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What do you want to do? Shall we go on a date with just the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.50,0:26:34.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… but…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.66,0:26:37.63,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.63,0:26:39.66,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,That's where the two of you have been!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.66,0:26:41.63,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Gosh, everyone's been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.23,0:26:42.93,Petto_basic_2,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Let's go, Hasumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.87,0:26:49.57,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I thought you'd left already, Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.91,0:26:51.94,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.28,0:27:01.48,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.00,0:27:03.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.81,0:27:28.11,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.54,0:27:30.11,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,For a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.48,0:27:33.01,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Carrying your luggage?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.01,0:27:33.85,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.38,0:27:37.09,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the free lessons. Aren't you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.49,0:27:41.09,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I have a rash, so just tell them I'm asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.79,0:27:44.76,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Are you avoiding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.59,0:27:49.00,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.70,0:27:58.41,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,How are things with you? And Junpei…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.00,0:28:07.00,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.02,0:28:17.66,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll skip lessons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.76,0:28:49.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't even go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.33,0:28:54.63,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder how Momo's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.67,0:28:59.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.50,0:29:04.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It seems I've had too much to drink, so I'll be going back to my room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.34,0:29:05.31,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.02,0:29:24.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I guess there won't be anyone around at this hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:47.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.60,0:30:03.33,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,First off, I have to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.30,0:30:07.04,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Mo—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.84,0:30:11.71,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Gosh…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.71,0:30:13.81,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,You're practicing after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.14,0:30:17.85,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,You're actually pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.32,0:30:23.18,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,You're too nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.19,0:30:28.96,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep, so I thought moving around would help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.26,0:30:33.70,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,You know… I like it when you look troubled like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.83,0:30:40.20,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Because you always act so happy-go-lucky and it pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.40,0:30:42.74,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.61,0:30:47.14,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Even though you're actually very lonely inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.21,0:30:50.35,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,You're the one who pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.40,0:31:09.00,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.13,0:31:10.16,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Just…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.16,0:31:12.50,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Just now, I thought I saw a woman outside the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.50,0:31:15.10,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.57,0:31:23.95,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh… come to think of it, the hall owner's daughter committed suicide a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.95,0:31:28.08,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Stop it! Don't tell scary stories like that at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.08,0:31:30.85,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go to sleep? You have to wake up early tomorrow anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.09,0:31:34.12,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,After hearing a story like that, I can't go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.00,0:31:41.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I had nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.76,0:31:43.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It seems like he's having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.70,0:31:51.97,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Even cats have a different home that the owner doesn't know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.97,0:31:54.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And Momo's a human after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.15,0:32:00.32,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Oh, a chick!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.65,0:32:02.82,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Hey, sweetheart, where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.79,0:32:06.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,A pet having a woman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.96,0:32:08.09,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.89,0:32:11.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's 10000 years too early for that brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.43,0:32:12.43,Petto_basic,man,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.56,0:32:18.63,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He doesn't even have money and has asthma. He can't even do anything on his own…!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.30,0:32:24.97,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Pets actually aren't as lonely as we think they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.97,0:32:29.11,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,I guess they have their own little world.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.92,0:32:41.09,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.09,0:32:42.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.33,0:32:49.46,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I was worried, so I came after you. But I lost sight of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.27,0:32:52.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.57,0:33:00.08,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No. I have to apologize for bringing you on a trip you didn't want to be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.38,0:33:02.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's not true…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.08,0:33:11.02,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But it makes me feel bad when your expression is like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.02,0:33:13.46,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no… I'm really fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.93,0:33:22.93,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.93,0:33:25.83,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I wonder how I can make you feel more at ease…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.27,0:33:29.54,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Can you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.24,0:33:33.38,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Hey, Takeshi…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.20,0:33:56.03,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.57,0:34:00.14,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait a second, Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.00,0:34:04.97,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Stop running away all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.90,0:34:28.40,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,Sorry, Junpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.33,0:34:34.37,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,But, deep down…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.37,0:34:37.71,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,deep down I like Takeshi after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.58,0:34:44.45,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,I like him so much I can't forget about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.98,0:34:51.32,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.54,0:35:19.88,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.88,0:35:21.85,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai, are you drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.38,0:35:24.02,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm not drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.09,0:35:27.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,We can't do this in a place like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.79,0:35:34.46,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then, can I stay over at your house when we get back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.46,0:35:37.13,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… but if it's too sudden, my pet…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.13,0:35:40.67,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Pets aren't allowed in your apartment, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.50,0:35:45.31,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,If you're so nice to your pet,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.61,0:35:49.48,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I may just get jealous of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.60,0:36:02.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Stop…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.10,0:36:26.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.52,0:36:31.19,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I just can't… in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.36,0:36:37.66,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.33,0:36:41.70,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You're right, not in a place like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.10,0:36:44.47,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I guess I am a little drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.47,0:36:47.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then I'll go buy some tea or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.84,0:36:48.94,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.94,0:36:52.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. It's just right here and I'm pretty thirsty too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.93,0:37:13.29,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Active, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.50,0:37:15.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.38,0:37:31.21,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What are you going to do tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.21,0:37:32.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.51,0:37:35.12,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,If Hasumi-kun's coming over, I can go somewhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:37.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why? Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.26,0:37:43.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's fine, I'll just turn him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.59,0:37:46.63,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it, I'll just disappear for a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.76,0:37:50.30,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? You don't have anywhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.83,0:37:53.27,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Of course I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.20,0:37:57.17,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's no problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.37,0:37:59.17,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,And I have some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.41,0:38:03.51,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Besides, I have these looks. So I'm sure there are a lot of people who'll be willing to feed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.88,0:38:07.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Even if I don't have you to look after me, I won't die or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.02,0:38:10.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.69,0:38:18.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then you don't have to come back for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.10,0:38:22.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.07,0:38:27.44,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Okay, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.67,0:38:34.34,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You can make out without worries… not in a place like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.78,0:38:37.75,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's probably a good idea to get sex out of the way as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.75,0:38:38.81,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.72,0:39:18.99,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.92,0:39:21.36,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.66,0:39:27.53,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Never come back, you stupid pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.70,0:39:33.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Stupid…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.85,0:39:46.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.09,0:39:57.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why did it turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.73,0:40:03.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,We've never gotten into a fight before.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.80,0:40:09.87,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You only have to say the words "Let's go home".
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.74,0:40:12.47,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Let's go home…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.07,0:40:14.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.14,0:40:18.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}If we had gone home then…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.35,0:40:21.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, you can't eat that until after dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.59,0:40:27.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right about now, as usual, we'd be…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.03,0:40:37.93,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That hurt, damn it…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.94,0:40:44.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.83,0:41:07.40,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.40,0:41:10.77,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,It's pretty hard to come back to work straight after a zengen.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.77,0:41:13.97,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,That's why I told you it wasn't worth going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.97,0:41:16.91,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,If it was only our department, we could have just gone over the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.27,0:41:19.41,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You're kidding me, Ishidacchi! You have to go for an interview now?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.41,0:41:21.68,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,You still smell like sake. Chew some gum.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.74,0:41:25.38,Petto_basic,boss2,0,0,0,,Hey, Uriyama! Uriyama, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.79,0:41:34.82,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Even if I don't have you to look after me, I won't die or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.59,0:41:37.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't come home!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.23,0:41:41.60,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Okay, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.51,0:41:53.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sure he's back home by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.01,0:42:00.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.02,0:42:03.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Today I don't feel so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.55,0:42:08.96,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see… all right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.06,0:42:14.26,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Rest well with Momo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.00,0:42:16.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.33,0:42:20.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.64,0:42:27.51,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}What he just said was ironic.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.35,0:42:37.72,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whatever it may be, there was no way such an odd lifestyle could continue like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.56,0:42:42.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}But now…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.73,0:42:45.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}On a day like this, when my head hurts…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.73,0:42:49.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to spend it with Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.30,0:42:58.57,note,text,0,0,0,,[sign]No pets allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.30,0:42:58.57,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,Hello, Iwaya-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.57,0:43:00.28,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,Were you on vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.08,0:43:03.91,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.78,0:43:07.52,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why aren't pets allowed?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.48,0:43:10.45,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh… Well, that's just a rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.50,0:43:11.50,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Shouldn't it be okay
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.65,0:43:13.62,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,if it doesn't cause anyone any trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.62,0:43:15.06,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why is it wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.32,0:43:16.52,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,Well, it's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.52,0:43:18.73,Petto_basic_ending,nanny,0,0,0,,Are you all right? You look a little sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.73,0:43:20.13,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,You don't have to say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.80,0:43:24.30,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,It's fine. If it's just fish or birds, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.30,0:43:28.04,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,However, other animals, such as dogs and cats,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.04,0:43:31.04,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,will damage the facilities on the premises.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.04,0:43:33.21,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,And they'll bark and bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.71,0:43:35.00,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.01,0:43:36.00,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.71,0:43:41.98,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,I understand. Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.52,0:43:47.46,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, Iwaya-san! I knew it! You have a pet, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.86,0:43:50.93,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, one human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.53,0:43:57.20,Petto_basic_ending,landlord,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.95,0:44:14.25,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Maybe she got pregnant…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.63,0:44:28.13,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess he's just not home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.12,0:45:28.96,note,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Momo\NLOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.52,0:45:28.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.67,0:45:41.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He really…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.01,0:45:49.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,He really won't come home…